Signed-off-by: Suren Baghdasaryan <surenb@google.com>
Reported-by: syzbot+b446dbe27035ef6bd6c2@syzkaller.appspotmail.com
Closes: https://lore.kernel.org/all/68794b5c.a70a0220.693ce.0050.GAE@google.com/
